### 1. 登录接口（获取 sessionId）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/atm/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cardNo": "6222020000000001",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 2. 账户信息查询接口
GET http://localhost:8080/api/atm/accounts/profile?sessionId=REPLACE_WITH_SESSION_ID

### 3. 余额查询接口
GET http://localhost:8080/api/atm/accounts/balance?sessionId=REPLACE_WITH_SESSION_ID

### 4. 退出登录接口
POST http://localhost:8080/api/atm/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "REPLACE_WITH_SESSION_ID"
}
